snippet.title: Little Cells - Android Trailer
snippet.description:
Google play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fullybugged.littlecells
Steam page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/352210
Other shops: http://littlecells.fullybugged.com:

"Little Cells" is a quick and simple puzzle action game, released on Windows, MacOs, Linux & Android devices.

Music by Jerome Angelot:
https://soundcloud.com/jerome-angelot
